labels/B-unstable", "name": "B-unstable", "color": "d304cb", "default": false, "description": "Implemented in the nightly compiler and unstable."}, {"id": 650731663, "node_id": "MDU6TGFiZWw2NTA3MzE2NjM=", "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/labels/C-bug", "name": "C-bug", "color": "f5f1fd", "default": false, "description": "Category: This is a bug."}, {"id": 900795185, "node_id": "MDU6TGFiZWw5MDA3OTUxODU=", "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/labels/A-const-eval", "name": "A-const-eval", "color": "f7e101", "default": false, "description": "Area: constant evaluation (mir interpretation)"}, {"id": 1472563007, "node_id": "MDU6TGFiZWwxNDcyNTYzMDA3", "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/labels/requires-nightly", "name": "requires-nightly", "color": "76dcde", "default": false, "description": "This issue requires a nightly compiler in some way."}], "state": "closed", "locked": false, "assignee": null, "assignees": [], "milestone": null, "comments": 19, "created_at": "2019-10-23T20:33:11Z", "updated_at": "2021-05-14T14:41:43Z", "closed_at": "2021-05-14T14:41:43Z", "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR", "active_lock_reason": null, "body": "[RFC 2203](https://github.com/rust-lang/rfcs/blob/master/text/2203-const-repeat-expr.md) specifically calls out `Vec::new` as a motivating example, however [this does not work](https://play.rust-lang.org/?version=nightly&mode=debug&edition=2018&gist=74b019cd4ec9d8656bf7197603fcab3c) on the current nightly.\r\n\r\n```rust\r\nfn main() {\r\n    let _: [Vec<i32>; 4] = [Vec::new(); 4];\r\n}\r\n```\r\n\r\nThere are two reasons for this. First, promotion in array repeat expressions currently uses the \"implicit\" rules for [promotability](https://github.com/rust-rfcs/const-eval/blob/master/promotion.md#implicit-and-explicit-contexts), which forbids promotion of function calls without `#[rustc_promotable]`. Second, the result of `Vec::new()` is marked as `NeedsDrop` since `Vec<T>` is `Drop`, which disqualifies it from promotion, even in an explicit context.\r\n\r\ncc #49147 ", "closed_by": {"login": "oli-obk", "id": 332036, "node_id": "MDQ6VXNlcjMzMjAzNg==", "avatar_url": "https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/332036?v=4", "gravatar_id": "", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/oli-obk", "html_url": "https://github.com/oli-obk", "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/oli-obk/followers", "following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/oli-obk/following{/other_user}", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/oli-obk/gists{/gist_id}", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/oli-obk/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/oli-obk/subscriptions", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/oli-obk/orgs", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/oli-obk/repos", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/oli-obk/events{/privacy}", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/oli-obk/received_events", "type": "User", "site_admin": false}, "reactions": {"url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/issues/65737/reactions", "total_count": 0, "+1": 0, "-1": 0, "laugh": 0, "hooray": 0, "confused": 0, "heart": 0, "rocket": 0, "eyes": 0}, "timeline_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/issues/65737/timeline", "performed_via_github_app": null, "state_reason": "completed"}